</tr><tr><td scope="row">Arkansas</td>
<td>Medicaid cost report:Â Â Â Number of staffÂ Â Â Hours workedMonthly reports (per shift, per day): Â Â Â CensusÂ Â Â Direct care staff hours Â Â Â Licensed staff hoursLinked to master facility database but not to MDS or OSCAR.</td>
